OL,3,CNHS home births suspended across
OL,4,CGloucestershire for at least six months
OL,6,FA suspension of NHS home births across
OL,7,FGloucestershire has been extended for
OL,8,Fat least another six months.
OL,10,FGloucestershire Hospitals NHS
OL,11,FFoundation Trust initially suspended
OL,12,Fhome births for two weeks at the
OL,13,Fbeginning of November, after staff
OL,14,Fraised safety concerns.
OL,16,FIt says it's now conducted a review
OL,17,Fand risk assessment of the service and
OL,18,Fneeds the time to retrain staff and
OL,19,Fdesign and implement a new model of
OL,20,Fcare.
