OL,6,FInterim Director of Midwifery, Heather
OL,7,FGallagher said, "Over the past two
OL,8,Fweeks the Trust has conducted a review
OL,9,Fand risk assessment of our home birth
OL,10,Fservice and it was clear that the
OL,11,Fsuspension needed to be extended to
OL,12,Fallow retraining, and a new model of
OL,13,Fcare delivery to be designed and
OL,14,Fimplemented.
